# SLAM DEMO

## Dependencies 

	```bash
	    sudo apt-get install ros-$ROS-DISTRO$-turtlebot-gazebo ros-$ROS-DISTRO$-turtlebot-indigo ros-$ROS-DISTRO$-turtlebot-simulator
	```
## Install

	```bash
	    cd catkin_ws/src
		git clone https://github.com/ShibataLab/Turtlebot-SLAM-Demo
		roscd catkin_ws
		catkin_make
	```
